{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"BMClpTRP3V8ITqM7R4kh0","title":"To Do List","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"type":"note","desc":"","links":[{"from":{"fname":"root","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":16,"column":1,"offset":477},"end":{"line":16,"column":9,"offset":485},"indent":[]},"value":"TODO"}],"anchors":{"main-thesis":{"type":"header","text":"Main Thesis","value":"main-thesis","line":8,"column":0},"cwf-project":{"type":"header","text":"CWF Project","value":"cwf-project","line":55,"column":0},"honours-thesis":{"type":"header","text":"Honours Thesis","value":"honours-thesis","line":70,"column":0}},"fname":"TODO","updated":1637563664481,"created":1635455071285,"parent":"PhD","children":[],"data":{},"contentHash":"5d67b35c4bda6790e5f1861897cf25c0","custom":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"to-do-list\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#to-do-list\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>To Do List</h1>\n<h2 id=\"main-thesis\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#main-thesis\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Main Thesis</h2>\n<p>Focus Question: How many factors are detected in the presences of breaks?</p>\n<p>Busywork</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Retroactively add pandoc citations, now that a way to get them is working is (kind of) available</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Theoretical</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Collate results representation theorems</li>\n<li>HI representation</li>\n<li>BKW representation</li>\n<li>come up with some examples</li>\n<li>See how this relates to <em>dynamics</em> in factors breaking</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Static Factors</p>\n<ul>\n<li>BNIC estimator</li>\n<li>AW estimator</li>\n<li>ON09 and ON10</li>\n<li>AHER and AHGR</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Dynamic Factors</p>\n<ul>\n<li>BN07</li>\n<li>DFM Function, using dpca, etc</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Backend Stuff</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Bessell Process p values, using strucchange::: (Hansen's approximation)</li>\n<li>Look into BP critical values and see if there are any implementations</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Break Date estimators</p>\n<ul>\n<li>BE Estimator (tedious)</li>\n<li>Han and Inoue HI</li>\n<li>BKW Baltagi (simple one and sequential one)</li>\n<li>CDG</li>\n<li>MS Ma and Su</li>\n<li>BHS (Bai, Han and Shi)</li>\n<li>DBH (QMLE)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Run the estimators across the dataset over time</p>\n<p>Type up AWS Guide</p>\n<h2 id=\"cwf-project\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#cwf-project\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>CWF Project</h2>\n<p>Constituent Methods</p>\n<ul>\n<li>FAAR</li>\n<li>FAAVAR </li>\n<li></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Simulation Study</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Type up formally, the one with multiple fixed <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>r</mi><mi>h</mi><mi>o</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">rho</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.69444em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">r</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">h</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">o</span></span></span></span></span> as constituent models</li>\n<li></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"honours-thesis\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#honours-thesis\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Honours Thesis</h2>\n<p>Not exactly sure how this can</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"backlinks\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#backlinks\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Backlinks</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/PhD\">PhD Homepage (vault)</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"